main event: A bright white glow with a white trail moved from north to south and then faded from view.
interesting points: The sighting lasted approximately 15-20 minutes., The object changed color from bright white to bluish white and then back to white., The object was larger and much brighter than a star., The altitude of the object was estimated to be 2000-3000 feet., No sound was heard during the sighting.
sighted object: bright white light changing to bluish white
